high_descs: Turn right and walk to the dresser with the plant on it.
Pick up the credit card by the plant.
Turn around and veer left to the couch.
Place the credit card on the couch to the right of the box.
Turn around and walk to the left side of the TV stand.
Pick up the credit card on the stand.
Turn around and walk back to the couch.

Near the back, there is a blue credit card. Pick it up.
Move across the room to the couch with the brown box on it.
Put the card down on the couch by the box.
Move across the room to the window with the TV in front of it.
Behind the TV there is a credit card on the stand. Pick it up.
Move back to the couch with the brown box.
Place the credit card on the left side of the box on the couch.
anns.task_desc: Gathering credit cards to a safer place.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the self past the coffee table.
Pick up the credit card on the shelf.
Take the credit card across the room to the sofa on the left.
Set the credit card down on the sofa between the box and the laptop.
Turn around and walk over to the TV stand.
Pick up the credit card on the TV stand behind the TV.
Turn and walk back across the room to the sofa.
Set the credit card down on the sofa to the left of the box.
anns.task_desc: Put two credit cards on the sofa.
